## Execution Checklist

- [ ] Plan read
- [ ] Baseline confirmed
- [ ] Scenario config confirmed
- [ ] Metrics confirmed
- [ ] Script path confirmed
- [ ] Output paths confirmed
- [ ] Report template confirmed
```

不得跳过 checklist 直接写代码。

------

### Step 2. 确认实现范围

确认 plan 中允许修改的文件范围。

通常允许：

```text
notebooks/scripts/chFusion_{topic}.py
src/ble_analysis/
